  "original_title": "\u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0d86\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dae\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d85\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db6\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dba: \u0db4\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0db7\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dba \u0d86\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dae\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0db8\u0daf?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka's economic crisis: How will the ongoing political instability affect the economy?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Central Bank Governor, Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe said in an interview with the BBC that everyone should understand the seriousness of the situation the country is in.",
        "He says that a stable political situation is definitely necessary to reduce the suffering of the people.",
        "\"There are only two ways to build this economy,\" the central bank governor explains.",
        "However, he emphasized that this step cannot be taken without political stability.",
        "As stated by the Central Bank Governor, if these measures fail, \"a situation where the people cannot live\" may arise in Sri Lanka."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Sri Lanka's",
          "label": "GPE"
        }
      ],
